<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>15</hymn_number>
<title>A SHELTER IN TIME OF STORM!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa I kiselnau, Suongpi,
 Huihpi nun tieng a I bitnau;
 Bangcheng hung mahleh bit hitiu,
 Huihpi nun tienga I bitnau.

[V2]
 Gam haksa ale Isu Suongpi ahi!
 Gam haksa ah, gam haksa ah;
 Gam haksa ale Isu Suongpi ahi,
 Huihpi nun tienga I bitnau!

[V3]
 2. Sun a lim nuom, zan a kulhpi,
 Huihpi nun tieng a I bitnau!
 Melma'n ei sulau tapuo'n a,
 Huihpi nun tienga I bitnau!

[V4]
 3. Huihpi hat in ei um kimvel,
 Huihpi nun tieng a I bitnau!
 I bitnau taihsan ngei puoi tiu,
 Huihpi nun tieng a I bitnau.

[V5]
 4. Aw Suongpi, Kulhpi deihum pen,
 Huihpi nun tienga ka bitnau!
 Ei panpihpa, hung nai zing uo,
 Huihpi nun tieng a ka bitnau!</lyrics>
</song>